column1: Table 4: Top 10 names for baby girls by region of usual residence of mother1,2,3, 2020

1 Births where the usual residence of mother was outside of England and Wales have been excluded from these figures. Of the 299,466 baby girls in the 2020 dataset, 56 were excluded because they were born to non-residents of England and Wales.
2 Births where the name was not stated have been included in the totals.
3 Figures are based on geography boundaries as of May 2021.
